prompts.user_prompt_template:
Generate a Personalized Study Plan for:

Name: {NAME}
Level: {LEVEL}
Week: {WEEK}
Track: {TRACK} (Core/Intensive)
Goal: {GOAL}
Strongest skill: {STRONGEST}
Weakest skill: {WEAKEST}
Recent scores: {SCORES}

Provide: daily_schedule (7-task breakdown with times), priority_focus (which task to spend extra time on), weekly_target (specific measurable goal), resources_recommended (from §7 content), adjustment_notes (what to change from default plan), motivation_message. Return JSON.
